column5: Do any of you know of any AA meetings in Kenora, Sioux Narrows or Nester Falls? If not, do you know of a number to call up there for meeting schedules? Thanks. Good fishing!
They have meetings in Sioux Narrows on Thursday nights at the church in town , You can call a guy called Wray at 226-4442 he will be able to give you time and details.
